---
import sobremi from '../assets/images/sobremi.webp';
---

<section
  class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center px-6 py-32 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div
    data-float-orb
    class="fixed top-1/4 -left-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-accent-orange/15 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    data-float-orb
    class="fixed bottom-1/4 -right-32 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-accent-purple/12 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    data-float-orb
    class="fixed -top-36 -right-20 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-accent-purple/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full flex items-center justify-between gap-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl text-center md:text-left">
      <span
        class="inline-block text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-accent-orange mb-8"
      >
        Creative Web Developer
      </span>

      <h1
        data-hero-heading
        class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4"
      >
        <span data-typewriter>Hola, soy Julián Recarte.</span>
        <span data-cursor class="inline-block ml-0.5 w-[3px] h-[1em] bg-accent-orange align-text-bottom"></span>
      </h1>
      <p
        data-hero-heading
        class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 text-copy/80 text-balance"
      >
        Convierto marcas en experiencias web interactivas para negocios que buscanPU destacar.
      </p>

      <p class="text-copy/60 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl">
        Llevo 3 años viajando y trabajando desde cualquier lugar del mundo.<br>
        Esa experiencia me enseñó que adaptarse no es improvisar, es encontrar
        la mejor solución con el contexto que tenés.<br>
        Lo mismo aplico a cada proyecto web que tomo: entiendo el negocio,
        el usuario y el objetivo antes de escribir una sola línea de código.
      </p>

      <div data-hero-buttons class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start items-center">
      <a
        href="#proyectos"
        data-magnetic
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-orange to-accent-pastel backdrop-blur-lg text-white rounded-full font-medium text-sm tracking-wider uppercase shadow-lg"
      >
        Ver proyectos
      </a>
        <a
          href="#contacto"
          data-magnetic
          class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-1/2 sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-sm tracking-wider uppercase overflow-hidden text-accent-orange hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300"
          style="border: 2px solid transparent; background-image: linear-gradient(#F2ECE4, #F2ECE4), linear-gradient(to right, #FF5C2B, #FFB088); background-origin: border-box; background-clip: padding-box, border-box;"
        >
          <span class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-orange to-accent-pastel opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></span>
          <span class="relative z-10">Contactar</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-0 right-[10%] w-1/2 max-w-lg">
      <img
        src={sobremi.src}
        alt="Julián Recarte"
        class="w-full h-auto block hero-img"
        loading="eager"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<style>
  .hero-img {
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to top, transparent 0%, black 33%, black 100%);
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to top, transparent 0%, black 33%, black 100%);
  }
</style>


